        <li>belongs to another person without permission</li>
        <li>violates trademarks or intellectual property rights</li>
        <li>is offensive, vulgar, or misleading</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You must notify us immediately of any unauthorised account use or
        security breach.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-[Bricolage Grotesque, sans-serif]">
