        or implied. We disclaim liability for any damages arising out of your
        use of the Service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-[Bricolage Grotesque, sans-serif]">
        11. Governing Law
      </h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of India. If any provision is found
        unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-[Bricolage Grotesque, sans-serif]">
        12. Changes to Terms
      </h2>
      <p>
        We may revise these Terms at any time. For significant changes, we will
